ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project focuses on analyzing the performance of marketing campaigns by evaluating their Return on Investment (ROI).
The goal is to help businesses identify which campaigns generate the highest returns and where marketing budgets can be optimized.
Using Power BI, this project transforms raw campaign data into an interactive and insightful dashboard that supports data-driven marketing decisions.

ğŸ¯ Business Objectives
Measure ROI for each marketing campaign
Compare campaign cost vs revenue
Identify high-performing and underperforming campaigns
Analyze campaign performance across channels and time periods
Support marketing teams in budget optimization
ğŸ§® Key Metrics (KPIs)
